Why are students encouraged to learn CS?
Students are encouradged to learn CS because our lives are starting to 
develop and envolve technology more often and frequently. So the older 
people/people who made it want us to understand how it works that way we can 
make it better and easier to use. For them And for us.

What should students learn from CS?
Students should in Cs how computers work and how to do other things on a 
computer than use google and play minecraft or CS Go. That way they can make 
it better and bigger to use.

